data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch home that combines comfort and coziness. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by abundance of natural light & a fireplace ready to be used during fall/winter season. Main floor layout connects the living room, updated kitchen with dovetail cabinet drawers, 3 bedrooms & full a bathroom with a jetted tub providing the perfect escape after a long day. The basement is clean and dry ready for your projects; be the host this coming-up holidays and impress your family and friends. Step outside to find a spacious backyard ideal for summer barbecues in addition to the 2.5 car garage. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home-sweet-home! Approved short sale being sold as is!
